oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Daniel Rothwell performs with Jackie Case and Danny Rothwell at the Museum of Appalachia Homecoming
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Old-time banjo player Daniel Rothwell is accompanied by Jackie Case on bass and his father, Danny Rothwell, during a performance at the Museum of Appalachia Homecoming, Norris, 2011.
Funding for this event was provided in part by a TAC Folklife grant.
